challengeName: CSFV Forums UI Prototype Update Part 4
detailedRequirements:
Task Overview

The goal of this challenge is to update the provided UI prototype as outlined below.

Task Requirements

  • Remove all notification popups related html tags from all pages in the header.
  • Fix the header widget in forums-thread.html and similar pages so that the tag does not overlap with title. It should push title to the right if the tag text is large/long.
  • Fix the thread message widget so that username (long ones) don't overlap with message area. It should push it.
  • It seems verigames prototype keeps loading and never ends as it is waiting for something to complete loading. Fix this issue.
  • The 6 prototypes attached in challenge forum are in scope

Deliverables

The updated UI prototypes with updated readme html file about change
